        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_723_115_2</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>Take a look: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0n5kwX5gkHc amp;list=UUq9oPCxcXnzTVl1s4c6iGkA amp;index=1 I am hoping that our era of **letting everyone in the universe down** is over.</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_723_115_3</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>But as LeVar Burton says, don't take my word for it.</TEXT>
        </DOC>
